text:
Alright, before we start this thing I want to share a quick story.

By the time we got to the point at which we were setting up Auth for our capstone project, I had *completely* forgotten what I had learned about it.

As a result, when I was trying to set up the part of the controllers to get the currently logged in user, I went searching the wrong guides for my solution.  I was looking for Auth in all the wrong places for two days.

Please please please do not neglect to get comfortable with this subject.
